# Build context is the repo root for every app (compose context: ../..), so this
# one file covers them all. node_modules / .next / the generated Prisma client are
# regenerated inside the build, never copied from context. Real .env* files are
# kept out of image layers; only the committed examples are let through.
**/node_modules
**/.next
**/src/generated
.git
**/.git
**/.env
**/.env.*
!**/.env.example
!**/.env.production.example
**/*.log
**/coverage
**/.turbo
**/*.tsbuildinfo
**/.DS_Store
